The paper deals with recommending related tables, which involves computing the similarity between tables. This task is related to information retrieval (IR) and database (DB) systems, as well as artificial intelligence (AI) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques for semantic representation and matching. The paper also mentions using a discriminative learning model, which falls under machine learning (LG) and computational linguistics (CL).
